Package: EVTxgboost
Title: Fitting Extreme-Value Theory (EVT) models with the xgboost algorithm
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonathan", "Koh", , "jonathan.koh@unibe.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7287-0588"))
Description: EVTxgboost is a simple R utility, designed as a package, whose goal is to fit models motivated by univariate and multivariate EVT using distributional boosting. The base algorithmic engine is the xgboost R library. 
